So the angle condition becomes, \frac{||a||.||b||}{||a.b||}=\frac{||b||.||c||}{||b.c||}
which just reduces to, ||a||.||c||= ||b||.||a.b||.\end{eqnarray*} Therefore, solving the equation for ||b|| gives us ||b|| = \frac{||a||.||c||}{||a.b||} = \frac{13\sqrt{10}}{17}. Consequently, the vector sum \mathbf{b} can be found by \mathbf{b} = \frac{\mathbf{a}}{||a||}\frac{||a||.||c||}{||a.b||} + \frac{\mathbf{c}}{||c||}\frac{||a||.||c||}{||a.b||} = \boxed{\frac{1}{17}(\begin{pmatrix} 7 \\ -4 \\ -4 \end{pmatrix} + \begin{pmatrix} -2 \\ -1 \\ 2 \end{pmatrix})}
